          "You have a secret friend, someone who still has their Avatar. Cultivate that relationship, it could be valuable."
        ],
        [
          "You have figured out that the clan keeps alive those who are useful. Perhaps you can translate your knowledge of Euthanatos magic into a new ritual or even Path?"
        ],
